TITLE: Using Arcjet Protect Function in Node.js
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the protect function to execute protection rules on incoming requests, including handling the decision and potential errors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/arcjet/arcjet-docs/blob/main/src/content/docs/reference/nodejs.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_4

