TITLE: Implementing Sliding Window Rate Limiting with Arcjet in Next.js
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to set up a sliding window rate limit rule that allows 100 requests in a 60-second window. The rule applies to all requests to /api/hello and is tracked by the client's IP address, providing a smoother rate limiting experience.
