    A[Client] -->|Request| B(Arcjet SDK)
    B --> C{Evaluate Arcjet Rules}
    C -->|Report| F[ Arcjet API]
    C -->|Previous decision
    read from cache| E[Application constructs response]
    E -->|"429 Too Many Requests Response"| A[Client]
```

