TITLE: Configuring Arcjet in Next.js Middleware (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of Arcjet in a Next.js middleware.ts file to run on all requests except static assets. This shows the TypeScript version of the middleware integration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/arcjet/arcjet-docs/blob/main/src/snippets/shield/reference/nextjs/Middleware.mdx#2025-04-12_snippet_0

