TITLE: Checking Rule Results for Missing User-Agent with @arcjet/inspect
DESCRIPTION: Alternative approach that uses the isMissingUserAgent function from @arcjet/inspect to check if a request is missing the User-Agent header after the Arcjet decision is made.
